{"tid":907961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★政府今午(19日)公布：香港貧窮人口達138萬 創9年新高","createTime":"2018-11-19T08:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T01:33:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b929e77f6fce22474a81e8c1b2a2f6ba6c004cc2","tid":907961,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:31:54.000Z","msg":"政府今午(19日)公布2017年香港的貧窮情況，在恒常現金福利未介入下，香港貧窮人口達138萬，貧窮率達20.1%，創下2009年以來、即9年新高，代表每5個香港人就有1個是貧窮，人數亦較2016年的135.2萬增加2%。<br />\n<br />\n身兼扶貧委員會主席的政務司司長張建宗表示，在經計及恒常現金津貼等政策介入後，貧窮人口達101萬，貧窮率為14.7%，較2016的99.6萬貧窮人口增加1.4%，張認為「升幅好少」。<br />\n<br />\n惟這是政府定出貧窮線以來，貧窮人口首度超越百萬人，加上政府過去每年不斷增加社福的開支幅度，令人質疑是愈扶愈貧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181119/photo/bkn-20181119141733406-1119_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181119162812\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181119%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181119141733406-1119_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181119162812&h=7d1d6d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181119/bkn-20181119141733406-1119_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181119%2Fbkn-20181119141733406-1119_00822_001.html&d=ZlhM6C4175W9et9oSJWY37%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3f5da62a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181119/bkn-20181119141733406-1119_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e671a84150ee8029e28097d2d63fda5c400bb610","tid":907961,"uid":131522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:32:57.000Z","msg":"睇下有幾多係個班大陸移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247211783c90621e3d236a5bac5e5fa4ed07d95b","tid":907961,"uid":194918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"佢點計先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多有資產新移民黎拎綜緩<br />\n貧窮人口唔高就奇"},{"pid":"7c720ca97ea10c31259e672b9894e3a9ec1993ce","tid":907961,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"777好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b7f68add3f1bece75427d96b3cf9b3b4af1393","tid":907961,"uid":189160,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:34:46.000Z","msg":"窮同富係相對既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最少錢果20%就叫窮架啦"},{"pid":"f81dec26e7e77054ec32363edd5e9b7f8baca870","tid":907961,"uid":131522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"247211783c90621e3d236a5bac5e5fa4ed07d95b","tid":907961,"uid":194918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"佢點計先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多有資產新移民黎拎綜緩<br />\n貧窮人口唔高就奇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"大陸幾層樓，幾塊地<br />\n政府收塊地又幾百幾千萬以上<br />\n然後走黎香港拎公營房屋同綜緩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea7fe829effc6c945d13530087c2d0822c0c3ec3","tid":907961,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"777<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb6cd1e35526934871166a8547dde7f22c190fc","tid":907961,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:36:41.000Z","msg":"每5個香港人就有1個是貧窮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e2fffeef61709f79a5fd6a97f58bdd67